    }
  },

  {
    \"item\" : \"Push yourself: Endure Harm (1 harm).\"
  },
  
  {
    \"item\" : \"Lose yourself: Endure Stress (1 stress).\"
  },
  
  {
    \"skill\" : {
      \"check\":\"false\",
      \"skill_text\":\"When you [i]Endure Harm[/i] in a fight, and your health is above 0, you may let the pain inflame your wildness (decide before rolling). If you then score a [b]strong hit[/b] and choose to embrace the pain, take +momentum equal to your remaining health. A weak hit counts as a miss.\"
    }
  }
  
